children.name: Login the NOP Admin site with <username>
Login the NOP Admin site with "admin@yourstore.com"
Given the user launches the NOPAdmin url
Then the user verifies the header text
When the user enters "admin@yourstore.com" in email webEdit
When the user enters "admin" in password webEdit
Then the user clicks on login button
Then the user verifies the homePage logo
And the user logouts the application
